{"tid":2061191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"26歲男偶像「猥褻騎上70歲阿嬤」！　壓倒硬上：親我一下…她拼死反抗受重傷","createTime":"2020-06-12T08:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T03:04:47.000Z","uid":33359,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"addf9d48a7d6f39d6249994544c95d22cd25dc76","tid":2061191,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"1.媒體來源:<br />\n<br />\nETtoday新聞雲<br />\n<br />\n2.記者署名:<br />\n<br />\n記者田暐瑋／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n3.完整新聞標題:<br />\n<br />\n26歲男偶像「猥褻騎上70歲阿嬤」！　壓倒硬上：親我一下&hellip;她拼死反抗受重<br />\n傷<br />\n<br />\n4.完整新聞內文:<br />\n<br />\n26歲男偶像「猥褻騎上70歲阿嬤」！　壓倒硬上：親我一下&hellip;她拼死反抗受重傷<br />\n<br />\n記者田暐瑋／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本男星山內大輔年僅26歲，外型帥氣，卻犯下惡劣罪行。今年1月某天凌晨，他闖入一<br />\n名70歲阿嬤家中猥褻，騎在對方身上要求親吻，阿嬤死命抵抗，骨盆處骨頭骨折，他隨後<br />\n洗劫阿嬤身上錢財逃之夭夭，過程全被監視器拍下，被警方逮捕歸案。<br />\n<br />\n這名70歲阿嬤在餐飲店打工，到了1月26日凌晨才下班回家，正在她進入家門準備上鎖的<br />\n瞬間，山內大輔突然衝出闖入，把她壓倒在地，整個人騎在她身上，並猥褻要求：「可以<br />\n親我一下嗎？」阿嬤拼死掙扎抵抗，導致骨盆處的骶骨重傷骨折。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4935/d4935113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4935%2Fd4935113.jpg&h=38004ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲山內大輔。（圖／翻攝自山內大輔推特）<br />\n<br />\n因為阿嬤不斷反抗，山內大輔最後索性搶走阿嬤包包逃之夭夭，裡面有6萬2000日幣（約1<br />\n萬7000元台幣）現金，阿嬤之後急忙向隔壁鄰居求助報警，警方根據附近監視器拍到的內<br />\n容鎖定山內大輔身份，11日將山內大輔逮捕歸案。<br />\n<br />\n對此，山內大輔所屬經紀公司表示，這次事件帶給社會極大的困擾，深深致上歉意，而他<br />\n也被公司除名，在官方網站中的藝人欄位中已找不到他的名字，他在案發後照常更新社群<br />\n網站，似乎並無悔意，消息曝光後引起廣大網友撻伐，認為他對70歲的老人家下手真的是<br />\n泯滅人性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4935/d4935114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4935%2Fd4935114.jpg&h=32c547b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲山內大輔。（圖／翻攝自山內大輔推特）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.完整新聞連結 (或短網址):<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1736133?redirect=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1736133%3Fredirect%3D1&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=31649ec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1736133?redirect=1</a>"},{"pid":"6d54c2b54fc1f25ee2eaccaa0c67be61ccfa972f","tid":2061191,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"上定囝"},{"pid":"a4f591de717d1d0d7f7d5c815f0218a7141b9d60","tid":2061191,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d54c2b54fc1f25ee2eaccaa0c67be61ccfa972f","tid":2061191,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"上定囝"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"我可以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5033f581158d3ef3ad7448fbe5e21f066aa5bc45","tid":2061191,"uid":206337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"屌嬤師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a3e7508504fbe804a2eb127f2a62856b67e7fa","tid":2061191,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a4f591de717d1d0d7f7d5c815f0218a7141b9d60","tid":2061191,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d54c2b54fc1f25ee2eaccaa0c67be61ccfa972f","tid":2061191,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"上定囝"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"我可以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"一起share吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a56114894bbc42187a2e54c911579d5f91d58ec","tid":2061191,"uid":16503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"以為印度新聞<br />\n<br />\n驅風師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class